929
00:37:06,580 --> 00:37:08,280
 znači, niko to slušao nije.

930
00:37:08,280 --> 00:37:10,120
 Nitko, niko nije.

931
00:37:10,120 --> 00:37:13,800
 Znali smo mi da postoji neka vesna zemijanac,

932
00:37:13,800 --> 00:37:14,900
 da imaju dva halda,

933
00:37:14,900 --> 00:37:16,020
 da ovo, da ono...

934
00:37:16,020 --> 00:37:17,780
 Ali to nitko stvarno nije slušao,

935
00:37:17,780 --> 00:37:20,140
 i onda jednostavno Zabranom,

936
00:37:20,140 --> 00:37:22,020
 to je postalo ultra popularno,

937
00:37:22,020 --> 00:37:24,440
 i evo ne da se poslijskorijen,

938
00:37:24,440 --> 00:37:26,040
 znači, to je invazivna vrsta,

939
00:37:26,040 --> 00:37:27,500
 taj turbo folk, ja ne znam.

940
00:37:27,500 --> 00:37:30,240
 Šta mislim, i sad, evo, ne znam,

941
00:37:30,240 --> 00:37:34,180
 čudo je kao Thompson napunio nešto u Zagrebu,

942
00:37:34,180 --> 00:37:37,160
 nije čudo kad napuni neka Aleksandra Prijević

943
00:37:37,160 --> 00:37:38,360
 razdužno opoštovanje,

944
00:37:38,360 --> 00:37:39,280
 pre mladoj dan,

945
00:37:39,280 --> 00:37:41,220
 ja nemam pojma šta je na pjevanica,

946
00:37:41,220 --> 00:37:42,220
 a kad za nju čuo,

947
00:37:42,220 --> 00:37:45,380
 dok nisi po portalima izišli vijesti,

948
00:37:45,380 --> 00:37:46,160
 kaže,

949
00:37:46,160 --> 00:37:48,180
 raspravdala arenu tri večeri,

950
00:37:48,180 --> 00:37:48,920
 ko?

951
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:50,440
 Mislim, ne zna ženu,

952
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:52,180
 nikad čuo za nju, nisam.

953
00:37:52,180 --> 00:37:54,140
 A što reče,

954
00:37:54,540 --> 00:37:56,360
 jedan odavde je on starac,

955
00:37:56,360 --> 00:37:58,460
 kaže, to sam skupio povim,

956
00:37:58,460 --> 00:38:00,520
 i ona ljudi i plakata zalijepio nije.

957
00:38:00,520 --> 00:38:03,500
 Mislim, danas su ti fenomeni malo drugačiji.

958
00:38:03,500 --> 00:38:04,200
 Istina.

959
00:38:04,200 --> 00:38:07,460
 Hvala se vrati na posušenja,

960
00:38:07,460 --> 00:38:09,400
 na županiju zapadno hercegašku.

961
00:38:09,400 --> 00:38:12,260
 Vi ste u posuškom vijeću,

962
00:38:12,260 --> 00:38:13,040
 kao HSS,

963
00:38:13,040 --> 00:38:14,640
 oporba svoje vrsta,

964
00:38:14,640 --> 00:38:15,120
 tako.

965
00:38:15,120 --> 00:38:18,660
 Imali vas u skupštini županije?

966
00:38:18,660 --> 00:38:19,600
 Nema,

967
00:38:19,600 --> 00:38:20,400
 nema,

968
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:21,460
 tu smo imali

969
00:38:21,460 --> 00:38:23,500
 jedno neugodno iskustvo,

970
00:38:23,500 --> 00:38:23,840
 znači,

971
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:24,400
 bili smo,

972
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:27,520
 dogovorili na zadnjim izborima,

973
00:38:27,520 --> 00:38:29,920
 koaliciju s HDZ-om na svim razinama,

974
00:38:29,920 --> 00:38:32,520
 i onda,

975
00:38:32,520 --> 00:38:34,680
 ovo je već za rubriku vjerovali,

976
00:38:34,680 --> 00:38:35,000
 ili ne,

977
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:35,380
 znači,

978
00:38:35,380 --> 00:38:37,180
 HDZ se nije držao dogovor.

979
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:39,100
 i onda,

980
00:38:39,100 --> 00:38:43,260
 kako smo dogovorili pozicije na listama,

981
00:38:43,260 --> 00:38:43,620
 znači,

982
00:38:43,620 --> 00:38:45,560
 koje bi pripadale HSS-u,

983
00:38:45,560 --> 00:38:46,940
 koje je HDZ-o,

984
00:38:46,940 --> 00:38:48,600
 onda su oni to htjeli mijenjati,

985
00:38:48,600 --> 00:38:50,760
 onda smo mi ju radili jedino,

986
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:52,000
 s naše strane,

987
00:38:52,000 --> 00:38:53,220
 što je bilo normalno,

988
00:38:53,220 --> 00:38:56,680
 nismo se jednostavno željeli plamirati,

989
00:38:56,680 --> 00:38:58,740
 nismo se željeli spuštati na tu razinu,

990
00:38:58,740 --> 00:39:01,520
 koalicija već bila potpisana,

991
00:39:01,520 --> 00:39:01,880
 ništa,

992
00:39:01,880 --> 00:39:02,820
 nek to stoji,

993
00:39:02,820 --> 00:39:04,620
 ko mala djeca,

994
00:39:04,620 --> 00:39:06,260
 mi se nećemo igrati sastaviti,

995
00:39:06,260 --> 00:39:07,200
 kako znate,

996
00:39:07,200 --> 00:39:08,960
 i tako da u ovom sazivu

997
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:11,140
 ne imamo nikoga u županijskoj skupštini,

998
00:39:11,140 --> 00:39:12,300
 ali evo, bože moj,

999
00:39:12,300 --> 00:39:13,320
 dogodne su izbori,

1000
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:15,220
 pa prvijen će se i to da će bović.

1001
00:39:15,220 --> 00:39:16,340
 Nije, pa dogodne su izbori,

1002
00:39:16,340 --> 00:39:17,740
 to se baš brzo bliže,

1003
00:39:17,740 --> 00:39:18,080
 vidim,

1004
00:39:18,080 --> 00:39:18,620
 recimo,

1005
00:39:18,620 --> 00:39:20,920
 i kod Srba i kod Bošnjaka,

1006
00:39:20,920 --> 00:39:22,680
 je predzborna kampanja već počela.

1007
00:39:22,680 --> 00:39:23,860
 I kod HDZ?

1008
00:39:23,860 --> 00:39:24,560
 Zar je?

1009
00:39:24,560 --> 00:39:26,020
 Pa kako nije,

1010
00:39:26,020 --> 00:39:28,260
 pa evo pričava sa izbornim zakonom.

1011
00:39:28,260 --> 00:39:29,960
 Pa kako nije priča,

1012
00:39:29,960 --> 00:39:34,020
 ako imate potpisan sporazum s partnerima,

1013
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:36,820
 u ovom slučaju to trojka i Rama,

1014
00:39:36,820 --> 00:39:39,100
 Isak i Elzina Pirići,

1015
00:39:39,100 --> 00:39:39,820
 koji je tu još,

1016
00:39:39,820 --> 00:39:42,380
 Sandi i Salkić imaju puno tih partnera,

1017
00:39:42,380 --> 00:39:46,700
 opet ima to malo seksualni konotacij,

1018
00:39:46,700 --> 00:39:48,020
 znači,

1019
00:39:48,020 --> 00:39:49,560
 ako imate dogovor s njima,

1020
00:39:49,560 --> 00:39:50,740
 da ste nakon u roku,

1021
00:39:50,740 --> 00:39:52,700
 pola godine izmijeniti izborni zakon,

1022
00:39:52,700 --> 00:39:54,800
 zašto niste kao uputili proceduru,

1023
00:39:54,800 --> 00:39:55,700
 nakon pola godine,

1024
00:39:55,700 --> 00:39:58,000
 zašto nakon dvi i po tri godine.

1025
00:39:58,000 --> 00:39:59,000
 To je pitanje za njih?

1026
00:39:59,000 --> 00:39:59,360
 Tako.

1027
00:39:59,360 --> 00:40:01,040
 To je za njih pitanje.

1028
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:01,820
 Jeste li ih pital,

1029
00:40:01,820 --> 00:40:02,900
 tojkada sam vam govorili?

1030
00:40:02,900 --> 00:40:03,680
 Jesam,

1031
00:40:03,680 --> 00:40:05,020
 pital sam ja svašta.

1032
00:40:05,020 --> 00:40:06,960
 Možda je bolje,

1033
00:40:06,960 --> 00:40:08,380
 evo i za moje mentalno zdrav,

1034
00:40:08,380 --> 00:40:09,380
 i za njihovo dane,

1035
00:40:09,500 --> 00:40:13,100
 sudjelo je sad u radu Hrvatskog narodnog sabora,

1036
00:40:13,100 --> 00:40:15,360
 jer ima običeva postaviti svakova pitanja,

1037
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:17,120
 svaki vrag me zanima,

1038
00:40:17,120 --> 00:40:19,920
 i moje misljenje nije konačno nikad,

1039
00:40:19,920 --> 00:40:21,500
 ja sam voljam promijeniti misljenje,

1040
00:40:21,500 --> 00:40:25,900
 ali uz ozbiljnu argumentaciju da mi neko obrazloši.

1041
00:40:25,900 --> 00:40:29,160
 Ali većinovna ta pitanja koja ja postavim,

1042
00:40:29,160 --> 00:40:31,060
 ostane samo mug s druge strane,

1043
00:40:31,060 --> 00:40:33,660
 neće ni da pokušaju odgovoriti,

1044
00:40:33,660 --> 00:40:35,560
 onda nešto nije u redu.

1045
00:40:35,560 --> 00:40:39,200
 Onda kad već i nakon te dvi i po tri godine

1046
00:40:39,200 --> 00:40:42,400
 uputiti taj zakon u proceduru,

1047
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:44,400
 zbog čega onda napuštanje sjednice,

1048
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:46,540
 u trenutku kad se treba glasati o njemu.

1049
00:40:46,540 --> 00:40:50,240
 Šta se onda to kaže?

1050
00:40:50,240 --> 00:40:51,600
 Prekin će on sjednicu,

1051
00:40:51,600 --> 00:40:52,720
 kaže glasati se sad.

1052
00:40:52,720 --> 00:40:55,400
 Alo, pa poslali zakon u proceduru

1053
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:56,340
 da se o njemu glasa.

1054
00:40:56,340 --> 00:40:59,320
 Pa kaže, možda ne bi prošao.

1055
00:40:59,320 --> 00:41:00,720
 Prvo, kako znaš.

1056
00:41:00,720 --> 00:41:03,020
 Drugo, pa ako ne bi prošao,

1057
00:41:03,020 --> 00:41:04,300
 pa znaćeš ko je protiv.

1058
00:41:04,300 --> 00:41:06,940
 Pa ćeš mu se revanširat,

1059
00:41:06,940 --> 00:41:08,900
 da možda nećeš imenovat,

1060
00:41:08,900 --> 00:41:10,320
 Bakira Hađe Omerovića

1061
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:12,100
 za ravnatelja federalne televizije.

1062
00:41:12,100 --> 00:41:14,700
 Ne, nisu to odlučili.

1063
00:41:14,700 --> 00:41:16,100
 Odlučili s pobići,

1064
00:41:16,100 --> 00:41:17,780
 znači, da ne glasaju o zakonu

1065
00:41:17,780 --> 00:41:19,820
 koji su oni uputili u proceduru.

1066
00:41:19,820 --> 00:41:22,100
 Ova Herceg-Bosanska četvorka,

1067
00:41:22,100 --> 00:41:24,260
 mi smo nešto razgovarao,

1068
00:41:24,260 --> 00:41:25,100
 razmišljali,

1069
00:41:25,100 --> 00:41:28,400
 postoje četiri varijante

1070
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:30,200
 izbornog zakona

1071
00:41:30,200 --> 00:41:32,320
 koje je Hrvatski Narodni Sabor

1072
00:41:32,320 --> 00:41:32,980
 pripremio,

1073
00:41:33,140 --> 00:41:34,840
 ova je predlog Marine Pendeš

1074
00:41:34,840 --> 00:41:36,160
 i jedna od tih varijanta.

1075
00:41:36,340 --> 00:41:39,380
 Mi smo uradili još jednu varijantu

1076
00:41:39,380 --> 00:41:40,640
 i ovo,

1077
00:41:40,640 --> 00:41:42,820
 ako se brzo ne raspetlja,

1078
00:41:42,820 --> 00:41:44,260
 teško da će se raspetljati,

1079
00:41:44,260 --> 00:41:45,240
 evo i ova sjednica

1080
00:41:45,240 --> 00:41:46,280
 koja vam trebala biti,

1081
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:47,360
 neće biti održana,

1082
00:41:47,360 --> 00:41:48,840
 vjerovatno,

1083
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:51,300
 mi ćemo uput svoj predlog zakona.

1084
00:41:52,180 --> 00:41:53,180
 gospodin Svitanović

1085
00:41:53,180 --> 00:41:54,740
 je to u ime ove četiri stranke

1086
00:41:54,740 --> 00:41:56,640
 uput i sigurno ćemo

1087
00:41:56,640 --> 00:41:58,020
 barem ostati na glasanju.

1088
00:41:58,020 --> 00:41:59,480
 Pa da vidimo ko će...

1089
00:41:59,480 --> 00:42:00,640
 Kako izgleda je predlog?

1090
00:42:00,640 --> 00:42:01,760
 Po čemu se razlikuje?

1091
00:42:01,760 --> 00:42:02,580
 Prekrasno,

1092
00:42:02,580 --> 00:42:03,760
 kako kaže Donald Trump.

1093
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:05,640
 Pa u principu

1094
00:42:05,640 --> 00:42:07,480
 zasniva se na elektorskim glasovima.

1095
00:42:07,480 --> 00:42:09,520
 Zasniva se na elektorskim glasovima.

1096
00:42:09,520 --> 00:42:10,980
 Zasniva se na to,

1097
00:42:10,980 --> 00:42:11,300
 ne znam,

1098
00:42:11,300 --> 00:42:13,020
 da bi HRŽ, ZHŽ,

1099
00:42:13,020 --> 00:42:15,980
 da bi davali veći broj elektora Hrvata,

1100
00:42:15,980 --> 00:42:17,360
 a davali bi, recimo,

1101
00:42:17,360 --> 00:42:19,320
 samo po jednog elektora Bošnjaka,

1102
00:42:19,320 --> 00:42:20,600
 dok bi, ne znam,

1103
00:42:20,660 --> 00:42:22,200
 iz Unskog stranskog kantona,

1104
00:42:22,200 --> 00:42:24,320
 davali veći broj elektora Bošnjaka

1105
00:42:24,320 --> 00:42:26,660
 i samo jednog elektora Hrvata,

1106
00:42:26,660 --> 00:42:28,440
 tako da se ne bi moglo dogoditi.

1107
00:42:28,440 --> 00:42:30,360
 I onda rješava i sljedić Finci

1108
00:42:30,360 --> 00:42:31,120
 i sve strane.

1109
00:42:31,120 --> 00:42:32,480
 Rješava apsolutno sve.

1110
00:42:32,480 --> 00:42:33,100
 Znači,

1111
00:42:33,100 --> 00:42:35,340
 sve se to spodi na to

1112
00:42:35,340 --> 00:42:37,640
 da se samo traže razloz

1113
00:42:37,640 --> 00:42:38,760
 zašto da se nešto

1114
00:42:38,760 --> 00:42:40,820
 ne implementira.

1115
00:42:40,820 --> 00:42:44,420
 Stranke, sve iz Republike Srpske

1116
00:42:44,420 --> 00:42:44,940
 su rekli,

1117
00:42:44,940 --> 00:42:46,140
 nama sve odgovara,

1118
00:42:46,140 --> 00:42:48,860
 mi ostavljamo direktan izbor.

1119
00:42:48,860 --> 00:42:50,320
 Ako hoćete,

1120
00:42:50,340 --> 00:42:52,060
 mi ćemo samo promijeniti,

1121
00:42:52,060 --> 00:42:53,320
 nek se promijeni ustav,

1122
00:42:53,320 --> 00:42:55,140
 Republika Srpska bira jednog.

1123
00:42:55,140 --> 00:42:57,280
 Po evo, koga godi zabere,

1124
00:42:57,280 --> 00:43:00,820
 sad i tu je jednostavan izlaz.

1125
00:43:00,820 --> 00:43:01,120
 Znači,

1126
00:43:01,120 --> 00:43:02,720
 Herceg-Bosna bira jednog,

1127
00:43:02,720 --> 00:43:04,520
 Saraj-Bosna bira jednog,

1128
00:43:04,520 --> 00:43:05,840
 svi se mogu kandidirati.

1129
00:43:05,840 --> 00:43:07,800
 Pa nek narod odluči,

1130
00:43:07,800 --> 00:43:08,060
 mislim,

1131
00:43:08,060 --> 00:43:08,820
 čemu je problem.

1132
00:43:09,060 --> 00:43:10,980
 nešto slično je pisao i ovaj

1133
00:43:10,980 --> 00:43:12,280
 Max Primorac,

1134
00:43:12,280 --> 00:43:14,860
 on je analitičar iz Heritage Foundation,

1135
00:43:14,860 --> 00:43:18,000
 Amerikanac je korijena iz Čitluka,

1136
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:18,620
 koliko vidim,

1137
00:43:18,620 --> 00:43:20,540
 i blizaki je Trumpovoj administraciji.

1138
00:43:21,340 --> 00:43:23,060
 Evo, on je baš objavio jedan nesaj

1139
00:43:23,060 --> 00:43:24,900
 u kojem poziva

1140
00:43:24,900 --> 00:43:26,960
 na ukidanje OHR-a,

1141
00:43:26,960 --> 00:43:28,900
 formiranje tri federalne jedinice.

1142
00:43:28,900 --> 00:43:30,720
 Evo, ovo sa neke njegove,

1143
00:43:30,720 --> 00:43:33,040
 ukratko, preporuke sam stavio na papir.

1144
00:43:33,040 --> 00:43:35,180
 Kaže, ukidanje OHR-a i bonskih oblasti.

1145
00:43:35,260 --> 00:43:38,960
 Uspostava tri federalne jedinice

1146
00:43:38,960 --> 00:43:40,340
 bez razmene teritorija,

1147
00:43:40,340 --> 00:43:42,780
 obnova prava Hrvatskog naroda

1148
00:43:42,780 --> 00:43:44,880
 na izbor legitimnih predstavnika,

1149
00:43:44,880 --> 00:43:47,780
 smanjenje utjecaja state departmenta

1150
00:43:47,780 --> 00:43:49,100
 i zamjena karijernih

1151
00:43:49,100 --> 00:43:50,940
 političkim diplomatima u regiji.

1152
00:43:50,940 --> 00:43:53,940
 Mi sad, nemo nikakvog veliposlanika američkog.

1153
00:43:53,940 --> 00:43:55,840
 Nemamo, ali inače,

1154
00:43:55,840 --> 00:43:56,420
 pravilo,

1155
00:43:56,420 --> 00:43:59,340
 politički diplomat američki

1156
00:43:59,340 --> 00:44:00,560
 ide u Zagreba,

1157
00:44:00,560 --> 00:44:02,720
 Beograd i Sarajevo

1158
00:44:02,720 --> 00:44:04,500
 dobijaju karijerne diplomate,

1159
00:44:04,500 --> 00:44:05,720
 znači, tu su oni

1160
00:44:05,720 --> 00:44:08,140
 nešto ko Jandroković

1161
00:44:08,140 --> 00:44:09,560
 u HDZ-u, koji valjaju

1162
00:44:09,560 --> 00:44:10,940
 svakoj administraciji

1163
00:44:10,940 --> 00:44:12,200
 i koji su tu samo, eto,

1164
00:44:12,200 --> 00:44:13,860
 da prođe vrijeme

1165
00:44:13,860 --> 00:44:16,460
 i tako da bi to imalo logike,

1166
00:44:16,460 --> 00:44:18,460
 iako ja mislim da Bosna i Hercegovina

1167
00:44:18,460 --> 00:44:19,740
 nije u fokusu

1168
00:44:19,740 --> 00:44:22,000
 definitivno američke administracije.

1169
00:44:22,000 --> 00:44:24,220
 Međutim, drago mi je da su odustali

1170
00:44:24,220 --> 00:44:25,520
 od svog projekta stvaranja

1171
00:44:25,520 --> 00:44:26,700
 Bosanske nacije,

1172
00:44:26,700 --> 00:44:28,500
 zbog koje smo mi završili

1173
00:44:28,500 --> 00:44:29,940
 u Bojluđačkoj košuljika

1174
00:44:29,940 --> 00:44:31,940
 koju smo završili.

1175
00:44:31,940 --> 00:44:34,000
 Sada treba će malo vremena

1176
00:44:34,000 --> 00:44:35,360
 dok u političkom Sarajevu

1177
00:44:35,360 --> 00:44:37,220
 se malo neskontaju,

1178
00:44:37,220 --> 00:44:38,340
 što se kaže u nas,

1179
00:44:38,340 --> 00:44:40,080
 da više ta priča

1180
00:44:40,080 --> 00:44:42,260
 o građanima baš i ne prolazi,

1181
00:44:42,260 --> 00:44:44,080
 jer nema baš tih nešto građana.

1182
00:44:44,080 --> 00:44:46,340
 I posljednji pop se pokazao,

1183
00:44:46,340 --> 00:44:47,260
 to je nešto mizirno,

1184
00:44:47,260 --> 00:44:49,760
 ispod 2% je bilo

1185
00:44:49,760 --> 00:44:51,100
 ostalih s tim,

1186
00:44:51,100 --> 00:44:52,480
 da su tu i Rumunji,

1187
00:44:52,480 --> 00:44:54,200
 Bugari i Črnogorci.

1188
00:44:54,200 --> 00:44:59,540
 Tako da, što se tiče tog narativa

1189
00:44:59,540 --> 00:45:00,640
 gospodina Primorca,

1190
00:45:00,640 --> 00:45:02,060
 da se apsolutno slaže s tim.

1191
00:45:03,180 --> 00:45:06,060
 slaže li se sa svečešnjim tvrdnjama

1192
00:45:06,060 --> 00:45:09,220
 da će se SDA triumfalno vratiti na vlast

1193
00:45:09,220 --> 00:45:10,080
 2.6.

1194
00:45:10,080 --> 00:45:11,700
 Apsolutno.

1195
00:45:11,700 --> 00:45:13,200
 Tu će dogoditi nešto

1196
00:45:13,200 --> 00:45:16,900
 slično ono što je se dogodilo u Hercegovini

1197
00:45:16,900 --> 00:45:18,660
 u 2014. godine.

1198
00:45:18,660 --> 00:45:22,700
 U 2010. godine su na izborima

1199
00:45:22,700 --> 00:45:25,840
 u Hercegovini možemo reći pobjedili

1200
00:45:25,840 --> 00:45:28,660
 HDZ 90 i HSP.

1201
00:45:28,660 --> 00:45:33,040
 I bili su u vlasti,

1202
00:45:33,040 --> 00:45:34,540
 rećemo konkretno u ZHŽ,

1203
00:45:34,540 --> 00:45:35,200
 u HDZ,

1204
00:45:35,200 --> 00:45:36,300
 bili u oporbi.

1205
00:45:36,300 --> 00:45:39,340
 U HNŽ je to bilo podijeljeno

1206
00:45:39,340 --> 00:45:40,740
 zbog drugačijeg odnosa

1207
00:45:40,740 --> 00:45:42,500
 sa našim federalnim partnerima,

1208
00:45:42,500 --> 00:45:43,560
 da ih tako nazove.

1209
00:45:43,560 --> 00:45:46,000
 I onda nakon

1210
00:45:46,000 --> 00:45:47,340
 kvalitete

1211
00:45:47,340 --> 00:45:49,860
 obnašanja funkcija

1212
00:45:49,860 --> 00:45:51,760
 90 i HSP-a,

1213
00:45:51,760 --> 00:45:53,760
 HDZ 92 i 14.

1214
00:45:53,760 --> 00:45:55,560
 Niči im izazavan vratio

1215
00:45:55,560 --> 00:45:57,480
 pomijel konkurenciju na izborima,

1216
00:45:57,480 --> 00:46:00,160
 jer ovi jednostavno nisu se pokazali

1217
00:46:00,160 --> 00:46:00,820
 dostojni,

1218
00:46:00,820 --> 00:46:01,820
 evo da ne upotrebi

1219
00:46:01,820 --> 00:46:03,480
 neku težuriju.

1220
00:46:03,480 --> 00:46:04,980
 Čisto će dogoditi sa

1221
00:46:04,980 --> 00:46:07,240
 strankom demokratske akcije

1222
00:46:07,240 --> 00:46:10,280
 i Bakir trenutno radi

1223
00:46:10,280 --> 00:46:12,000
 najpametnije što može šuti,

1224
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:13,220
 bježi od medija,

1225
00:46:13,220 --> 00:46:14,840
 jer što manje progovara,

1226
00:46:14,840 --> 00:46:16,420
 na više će glasova dobit,

1227
00:46:16,420 --> 00:46:18,340
 a svaki istup, ne znam,

1228
00:46:18,340 --> 00:46:20,200
 od Rame, Isaka,

1229
00:46:20,200 --> 00:46:21,560
 Adnana, Delića,

1230
00:46:21,560 --> 00:46:23,720
 Nervina, Nikšća,

1231
00:46:23,720 --> 00:46:25,040
 koji kaže da ljudi

1232
00:46:25,040 --> 00:46:27,120
 koji zaviske grivu se klimama

1233
00:46:27,120 --> 00:46:28,240
 na ovim vrućinama,

1234
00:46:28,240 --> 00:46:31,020
 mislim da donosi vrećom glasove

1235
00:46:31,020 --> 00:46:32,660
 stranke demokratske akcije.

1236
00:46:32,660 --> 00:46:35,080
 što mislite u Republike Srpske,

1237
00:46:35,080 --> 00:46:35,720
 kako će izgledati,

1238
00:46:35,720 --> 00:46:36,800
 hoće uspjeti SNSD?

1239
00:46:36,800 --> 00:46:38,900
 SNSD će pobijediti.

1240
00:46:38,900 --> 00:46:40,380
 Što znači,

1241
00:46:40,380 --> 00:46:42,920
 na 26. čeka SNSD,

1242
00:46:42,920 --> 00:46:44,720
 SDA i Upitnik?

1243
00:46:45,180 --> 00:46:46,340
 Pa evo, vidit ćemo,

1244
00:46:46,340 --> 00:46:47,800
 ne znam,

1245
00:46:47,800 --> 00:46:48,340
 ja baš,

1246
00:46:48,340 --> 00:46:50,860
 pitanje koalicijskog potencijala

1247
00:46:50,860 --> 00:46:53,580
 je uvijek vrlo interesantno pitanje.

1248
00:46:53,580 --> 00:46:56,840
 Što se tiče grupacije ove četiri stranke,

1249
00:46:56,840 --> 00:46:57,600
 znači,

1250
00:46:57,720 --> 00:47:00,060
 naš prvi partner za razgovor

1251
00:47:00,060 --> 00:47:02,080
 da biće HDZ Bosne i Hercegovine.

1252
00:47:02,080 --> 00:47:05,040
 Mislimo da uz dogovor

1253
00:47:05,040 --> 00:47:07,980
 nas i HDZ-a

1254
00:47:07,980 --> 00:47:09,000
 možemo osigurati

1255
00:47:09,000 --> 00:47:10,320
 neprobovenu poziciju

1256
00:47:10,320 --> 00:47:11,920
 svome narodu političku.

1257
00:47:11,920 --> 00:47:14,960
 Tek ako ne uspijemo dođi

1258
00:47:14,960 --> 00:47:16,520
 do dogovora s HDZ-om,

1259
00:47:16,520 --> 00:47:18,100
 ako nam narod dani

1260
00:47:18,100 --> 00:47:20,820
 dovoljno političkog legitimiteta,

1261
00:47:20,820 --> 00:47:22,780
 vidit ćemo postoj

1262
00:47:22,780 --> 00:47:24,580
 neka druga varijanta

1263
00:47:24,580 --> 00:47:26,640
 u slučaju da ne dobijemo

1264
00:47:26,640 --> 00:47:28,800
 dovoljno političkog legitimiteta,

1265
00:47:28,800 --> 00:47:29,740
 nećemo sigrati,

1266
00:47:29,740 --> 00:47:31,100
 ostaj ćemo opozicija

1267
00:47:31,100 --> 00:47:33,020
 i nek se stavlja ako može,

1268
00:47:33,020 --> 00:47:33,640
 Bože moj.

1269
00:47:33,640 --> 00:47:34,880
 Gospodin Karamoć,

1270
00:47:34,880 --> 00:47:36,920
 hvala vam na ovom gostovanju.

1271
00:47:36,920 --> 00:47:38,520
 Hvala vama što ste nas pratili,

1272
00:47:38,520 --> 00:47:39,560
 nadam se da vam je

1273
00:47:39,560 --> 00:47:41,620
 bilo korisno i zanimljivo.

1274
00:47:41,620 --> 00:47:45,480
 2025-a je prošla već svoju sredinu,

1275
00:47:45,480 --> 00:47:46,980
 26. izborna godina,

1276
00:47:46,980 --> 00:47:48,200
 biće asfaltiranja,

1277
00:47:48,200 --> 00:47:49,640
 biće i fajtanja, čini mi se.

1278
00:47:49,640 --> 00:47:50,360
 Biće svega,

1279
00:47:50,360 --> 00:47:51,400
 biće rasvijete,

1280
00:47:51,400 --> 00:47:52,880
 biće Ševapa,

1281
00:47:52,880 --> 00:47:54,080
 biće točene pire,

1282
00:47:54,240 --> 00:47:55,700
 tako da biće zanimljivo.

1283
00:47:55,700 --> 00:47:57,940
 Evo je naša predzadnja epizoda

1284
00:47:57,940 --> 00:47:59,340
 u ovoj sezoni,

1285
00:47:59,340 --> 00:48:00,840
 u sljedećoj epizodi

1286
00:48:00,840 --> 00:48:02,160
 imamo još jednog zanimljivog

1287
00:48:02,160 --> 00:48:03,480
 i ekskluzivnog gosta,

1288
00:48:03,480 --> 00:48:05,520
 tako da pratite potrast Herceguna.

1289
00:48:05,520 --> 00:48:06,180
 Lijep pozdrav!

